* BMAP phase-8 cross-reference (run with the XR option): the listing gains a
* statement-number column, and a cross-reference table lists each symbol's
* value, definition line (marked *), and the lines that reference it.
       OUNAME XREFT
KON    EQU    5
START  LDA    KON
       ADA    KON
       STA    START
LOOP   LDQ    LOOP
       TRA    START
       END
